AdminGroup, MemberGroup
public abstract class SystemGroup
extends Group

Base class for all system-wide groups, that is, the groups that are managed by a system administrator.
Groups categories:

  • system-wide: member, admin and broker groups.
  • Others: operator groups (these groups are managed by the owner member).

ameyer
